OL,3,CNew head coach embraces Liverpool's
OL,4,C'magic' and vows to stay true to
OL,5,Chimself
OL,7,FLiverpool FC's new head coach says he
OL,8,Fis determined to soak up the "magic"
OL,9,Fof his new job and insists he won't
OL,10,Flet the pressure change who he is.
OL,12,FAndoni Iraola arrives at Anfield after
OL,13,Fa successful stint at Bournemouth,
OL,14,Fstepping into one of the most high-
OL,15,Fprofile roles in English football.
OL,17,FHe replaces Arne Slot, who was sacked
OL,18,Fjust a year after guiding the Reds to
OL,19,Fthe Premier League title in his first
OL,20,Fcampaign as head coach.
OL,26,@pD@^OUpD@dO]
