PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784060308
OL,3,CNew head coach embraces Liverpool's
OL,4,C'magic' and vows to stay true to
OL,5,Chimself
OL,7,FSpeaking for the first time, Iraola
OL,8,Facknowledged the scrutiny that comes
OL,9,Fwith the Liverpool hot seat, but says
OL,10,Fhe will face it head-on.
OL,12,FHe said: "I understand this is a
OL,13,Fmassive club. Everything I'm going to
OL,14,Fsay now is going to get the biggest
OL,15,Fscrutiny.
OL,17,F"You have to be very aware of the
OL,18,Fmistakes but I wouldn't like to be too
OL,19,Fcareful."
OL,26,@tD@JOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
