CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784060308
OL,3,CNew head coach embraces Liverpool's
OL,4,C'magic' and vows to stay true to
OL,5,Chimself
OL,7,FUnlike his predecessor, Iraola says he
OL,8,Fis keen to immerse himself fully in
OL,9,Fthe life of the city.
OL,11,FWhile Slot commuted from near
OL,12,FManchester Airport to be closer to
OL,13,Ffamily in the Netherlands, the Basque-
OL,14,Fborn coach says he wants to experience
OL,15,FLiverpool to the fullest.
OL,17,F"I'm not going to live in my bubble,
OL,18,Fjust training ground, home. I would
OL,19,Flike to go to the city, experience the
OL,20,Fcity," he said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784060308
OL,3,CNew head coach embraces Liverpool's
OL,4,C'magic' and vows to stay true to
OL,5,Chimself
OL,7,F"But it's part of the magic of being
OL,8,Fthe Liverpool manager and I would like
OL,9,Fnot to change too much."
OL,11,FIraola's first job will be to re-
OL,12,Fenergise a Liverpool squad that
OL,13,Fslumped to fifth last season, just
OL,14,Fmonths after their historic title win.
OL,16,FWith star names like Mo Salah and Andy
OL,17,FRobertson departing this summer, he
OL,18,Fsays he knows there is plenty of work
OL,19,Fto do, both on and off the pitch.
OL,26,@qD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784060308
OL,3,CNew head coach embraces Liverpool's
OL,4,C'magic' and vows to stay true to
OL,5,Chimself
OL,7,FHe said: "We've signed two players
OL,8,Falready but we need more. I want the
OL,9,Fplayers here from day one, ready to
OL,10,Ftrain for pre-season, but I understand
OL,11,Ffootball doesn't work like this.
OL,13,F"The club is working hard for new
OL,14,Fsignings and I'm trying to help too,"
OL,16,FDespite the challenge, Iraola says his
OL,17,Fphilosophy won't change. He said: "I
OL,18,Ftalked to the players and staff about
OL,19,Fthe things that weren't working and
OL,20,Fthings we think we can do differently.
OL,26,@oD@JOUvD@eO]yD@cOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784060308
OL,3,CNew head coach embraces Liverpool's
OL,4,C'magic' and vows to stay true to
OL,5,Chimself
OL,7,F"I have the advantage that the players
OL,8,Falready know what we are going to
OL,9,Fdemand in terms of style of play, but
OL,10,Fwe will have time to know each other."
OL,12,FAbove all, Iraola wants to deliver a
OL,13,Fbrand of football that reconnects the
OL,14,Fteam with the Anfield faithful.
OL,26,@rD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784060308
OL,3,CNew head coach embraces Liverpool's
OL,4,C'magic' and vows to stay true to
OL,5,Chimself
OL,7,FHe said: "Football, and especially
OL,8,FLiverpool, is about connecting:
OL,9,Fconnecting with the people, connecting
OL,10,Fwith our supporters. We have to be a
OL,11,Fteam that works hard, is intense,
OL,12,Faggressive, and vertical, so everyone
OL,13,Fcan feel comfortable supporting this
OL,14,Fteam."
OL,16,FLiverpool fans will be hoping Iraola's
OL,17,Fapproach brings both stability and
OL,18,Fexcitement back to Anfield and that he
OL,19,Fcan write the next chapter in the
OL,20,Fclub's storied history.
OL,26,@oD@JOUvD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
